description:
UeCC: Table storing User Equipment Cell Connection (UeCC) data including timestamp, location, cell identifier, and associated identifiers for Ericsson-specific attributes.
- dateTime: Timestamp of the UeCC record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell tower.
- Id2: Redundant or alternative identifier for the cell tower.
- Id3:  Likely a secondary identifier, possibly related to a specific UeCC instance within the cell.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier specifying this as UeCC data.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific attribute format.
- UeCC.ueCCId: Unique identifier for this specific UeCC instance.
